OL,3,CTeenage boys found guilty of murdering
OL,4,C'loving father'
OL,6,FTwo teenage boys have been found
OL,7,Fguilty of murdering a "loving" husband
OL,8,Fand father who was stabbed to the
OL,9,Fheart with a kitchen knife.
OL,11,FThe 17 and 16-year-old boys, who
OL,12,Fcannot be named because of their age,
OL,13,Fhad denied the murder of Kamran Rasool
OL,14,FAman, 38, but admitted his
OL,15,Fmanslaughter.
OL,17,FA jury at Cardiff Crown Court
OL,18,Fdelivered a unanimous verdict on
OL,19,FTuesday, 23 December.
