OL,3,CTeenage boys found guilty of murdering
OL,4,C'loving father'
OL,6,FThe teenagers will be sentenced on 20
OL,7,FFebruary.
OL,9,FThe court heard that both teenagers
OL,10,Fhad been drinking throughout the day,
OL,11,Fand the 16-year-old defendant "swore
OL,12,Fon his dead granddad's grave he would
OL,13,Fstab and murder".
OL,15,FProsecutor Owen Edwards KC said the
OL,16,Fincident began when the 16-year-old
OL,17,Flooked out of the window of a property
OL,18,Fin Barry Road and saw Mr Aman getting
OL,19,Finto his Volkswagen Passat, and
OL,20,Fbriefly looked at him.
