OL,3,CTeenage boys found guilty of murdering
OL,4,C'loving father'
OL,6,FThe defendant shouted, "What you
OL,7,Flooking at bro?" and began punching
OL,8,Fhis own head. The 16-year-old said he
OL,9,Fwas "going to beat people up" and the
OL,10,F17-year-old responded: "Come on bro,
OL,11,Flet's go, I'll back you".
OL,13,FThe 16-year-old ran to Mr Aman's car
OL,14,Fand tried opening the locked passenger
OL,15,Fdoor.
OL,17,FMr Edwards said: "Kamran had done
OL,18,Fnothing to invite trouble. Kamran did
OL,19,Fnot know (the defendants).
