OL,4,C'loving father'
OL,6,FUpon getting out of his car, Mr Aman
OL,7,Fwas confronted by the 16-year-old and
OL,8,Fpunched in the face. The two exchanged
OL,9,Fblows.
OL,11,FThe 17-year-old returned to the house
OL,12,Fin Barry Road and retrieved a kitchen
OL,13,Fknife before returning to the scene.
OL,15,FNeighbours were alerted to the
OL,16,Fincident in the street and made
OL,17,Fattempts to intervene, as Mr Aman was
OL,18,Fpushed into a neighbouring property
OL,19,Fwith the defendants in pursuit.
