OL,3,CTeenage boys found guilty of murdering
OL,4,C'loving father'
OL,6,FMr Edwards said: "As (the 16-year-old)
OL,7,Fpunched him, (the 17-year-old)
OL,8,Frepeatedly tried to stab him.
OL,10,F"He succeeded with a single blow which
OL,11,Fpenetrated his heart.
OL,13,F"The two young men left Kamran to
OL,14,Fbleed to death on the pavement while
OL,15,Fconcerned neighbours did all they
OL,16,Fcould to assist Kamran."
OL,18,FDespite attempts to save Mr Aman, he
OL,19,Fwas pronounced dead at 1.07am.
