OL,3,CTeenage boys found guilty of murdering
OL,4,C'loving father'
OL,6,FBoth defendants fled the scene and
OL,7,Fwere later arrested in Court Road.
OL,9,FIn prepared statements, both teenagers
OL,10,Fdenied responsibility for causing Mr
OL,11,FAman's murder. Neither gave evidence
OL,12,Fat trial and both were found guilty of
OL,13,Fmurder by the jury.
OL,15,FIn a statement previously issued by Mr
OL,16,FAman's family, they said: "A devoted
OL,17,Fhusband, a loving father, a cherished
OL,18,Fson, brother, uncle and loyal friend,
OL,19,FKamran was the heart of his family and
OL,20,Floved within his community," they said.
