OL,3,CTeenage boys found guilty of murdering
OL,4,C'loving father'
OL,6,F"Known for his generous spirit and
OL,7,Fkind heart, Kamran brought warmth and
OL,8,Fstrength to everyone he met.
OL,10,F"His absence leaves an immeasurable
OL,11,Fvoid in the lives of all who knew him.
OL,13,F"As we grieve this unimaginable loss,
OL,14,Fwe also honour and celebrate the life
OL,15,Fhe lived and the impact he made.
OL,17,F"May his memory be a blessing."
